replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71da272e9ee4da69bae029de0d32263062f45485","tid":2329788,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"好似呈堂閉路影到香港警魔打已制伏的群眾<br />\n<br />\n香港警魔一聲唔記得/唔清楚就法官同政府扮傻唔追究<br />\n<br />\n一直都話係香港套標準經常搬龍門"},{"pid":"b6be55a25460d9e97cf761299543fa7499368813","tid":2329788,"uid":124663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"打暈左捉實佢對手拉起佢 推佢落樓"},{"pid":"dba8088426a2fb23c794feba4a1c1c0d3292d1dc","tid":2329788,"uid":152387,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"邊有人會用掌心擋狗棍<br />\n而且本能反應係會舉手臂擋,身體其他部位好有機會出現明顯瘀痕<br />\n<br />\n呢個動作就有機會掌心瘀,但手背照理應該都有機會擦損?<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQRmWPYEnQxxP2uAieoz-PO5RqNVMnqhE63BA&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQRmWPYEnQxxP2uAieoz-PO5RqNVMnqhE63BA%26usqp%3DCAU&h=df8098e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1292704833443524608/IAuPYoj9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2F1292704833443524608%2FIAuPYoj9.jpg&h=b1590a4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ece955c9cebb6636a4afead21accd7916d021d3","tid":2329788,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6a177416cb2a0820b92df058d9ad003e977161","tid":2329788,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s